sources.title: Girl Madness (1961 film) Directed by Coleman Francis with Tor Johnson  | Horror, Sci-Fi
sources.description:
From the desert's depths, terror rises!
A group of scientists and military personnel must confront a monstrous, radiation-mutated creature terrorizing the remote Yucca Flats after a nuclear test goes horribly wrong.

Original title: The Beast of Yucca Flats (1961)
Directed and Written by Coleman Francis

Main cast:
Tor Johnson - Joseph Javorsky / The Beast
Douglas Mellor - Hank Radcliffe
Barbara Francis - Lois Radcliffe
Bing Stafford - Jim Archer
Larry Aten - Joe Dobson
Ronald Francis - Randy Radcliffe
Alan Francis - Art Radcliffe
Jim Oliphant - Vacationing Husband
Linda Bielema - Vacationing Wife
Anthony Cardoza - KGB Driver / Helpful Neighbor
Conrad Brooks - Man at Airfield

Black & White version: https://youtu.be/BNgDFxKU4xI
